Invocation Name: note my strings
des: Identify notes of your fretted instrument in the tuning of your choice. Strive to acheive a high score every session. Guitar, Ukulele, Banjo, Bass, and Mandolin default to the standard tunings. Customized tuning is supported and remembered between games.
